name: DeathMatch at the Space Station
description: Having cruised thourgh Hell, taken a couple of planets, etc., it's now time to show where your friends' bodies belong. Let the CARNAGE begin! This DeathMatch ONLY level, gives you the chance to make them end up like one of those bodies on a stick! The level features a space-station like evironment. It's complete with a POW jail, a landing pad, and service station.
